ength scale.pdf;/Users/michelecastellana/Zotero/storage/JIQUFIPP/Baity-Jesi et al. - 2023 - Memory and rejuvenation effects in spin glasses are governed by more than one length scale.pdf;/Users/michelecastellana/Zotero/storage/JPRQ9PDK/Baity-Jesi et al. - 2023 - Memory and rejuvenation effects in spin glasses are governed by more than one length scale.pdf;/Users/michelecastellana/Zotero/storage/MCN785WS/Baity-Jesi et al. - 2023 - Memory and rejuvenation effects in spin glasses are governed by more than one length scale.pdf;/Users/michelecastellana/Zotero/storage/QZK2JUUW/Baity-Jesi et al. - 2023 - Memory and rejuvenation effects in spin glasses are governed by more than one length scale.pdf;/Users/michelecastellana/Zotero/storage/T49G6QLX/Baity-Jesi et al. - 2023 - Memory and rejuvenation effects in spin glasses are governed by more than one length scale.pdf;/Users/michelecastellana/Zotero/storage/T7YBV6XK/Baity-Jesi et al. - 2023 - Memory and rejuvenation effects in spin glasses are governed by more than one length scale.pdf;/Users/michelecastellana/Zotero/storage/TG43PK99/Baity-Jesi et al. - 2023 - Memory and rejuvenation effects in spin glasses are governed by more than one length scale.pdf;/Users/michelecastellana/Zotero/storage/WAYQ5UKT/Baity-Jesi et al. - 2023 - Memory and rejuvenation effects in spin glasses are governed by more than one length scale.pdf;/Users/michelecastellana/Zotero/storage/ZFS2YPZJ/Baity-Jesi et al. - 2023 - Memory and rejuvenation effects in spin glasses are governed by more than one length scale.pdf;/Users/michelecastellana/Zotero/storage/ZJ7CIQMV/Baity-Jesi et al. - 2023 - Memory and rejuvenation effects in spin glasses are governed by more than one length scale.pdf}\n}\n","metadata":{"DeclarePrefChars":"","noopsort":false,"packages":[]},"meta":{"revision":0,"created":1751534255903,"version":0,"updated":1753730283776},"$loki":1062},{"exportNotes":false,"useJournalAbbreviation":true,"bibtexURL":"off","DOIandURL":"both","itemID":26249,"e